               <p>Counsel for the prosecution.</p>

               <p>Mr. Silvester.</p>

               <p>Mr. Garrow.</p>

               <p>No counsel for the defendant.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900710-1-person39">
                  John
                   Tronson
               <interp inst="t17900710-1-person39" type="surname" value="Tronson"></interp>
